.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, plum
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis, lily, bellflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, electrician, musician, software-developer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rowing, tennis
 1. the person who growslily is not the dancer##6
 2. the software-developer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person eating plum is the musician##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the dancer and the electrician##2
 5. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the software-developer##1
10. the electrician is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the dancer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
14. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
