There are 4 different nationalities: british, malaysian, polish, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
 2. the russian is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 8. the malaysian is the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
10. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
14. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
