 7. the dutch is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 8. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the videographer##8
 9. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the fan of reggae##7
10. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the pakistani##8
11. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
12. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the fan of d&b##8
13. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
14. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
15. the indian is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5

