.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, badminton, basketball
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, hiking, skydiving, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, librarian, social-worker, videographer
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, taxi, trike
 1. the librarian is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 2. the person driving the airplane is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
 3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 4. the social-worker is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's sport is lacrosse##7
 7. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
 8. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
 9. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
10. the librarian is not to the left of the librarian##8
11. the electrician is on the far left##1
12. the videographer is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
15. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5
16. the librarian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4       |
| Sport    | lacrosse        | swimming      | basketball      | badminton          |
| Hobby       | video-games | skydiving     | card-games | hiking       |
| Job         | electrician | social-worker | librarian  | videographer |
| Transport   | taxi        | trike         | bus        | airplane     |

