The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, taxi, train, trike
 1. the owner of the goldfish is not the fan of rock##6
 2. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the person driving the taxi##7
 3. the townhouse house is the fan of punk##1
 4. the victorian house is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
 5. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the train and the fan of salsa##2
 6. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 8. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
 9. the person driving the taxi is not the owner of the goldfish##6
10. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
11. the victorian house is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
13. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
14. the fan of folk is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
